card.name: Battle Footballer
card.description: A cyborg with high defense power. Originally it was invented for a football machine.

card.name: Blazing Inpachi
card.description: A wicked wooden spirit now burning in flames. Its fire attack is powerful, but it will soon be nothing but ashes.

card.name: Tune Warrior
card.description: The warrior's antenna can attune it to any energy wave. It can monitor transmissions from miles away but always suffers from bad reception.

card.name: Rapid Warrior
card.description: During your Main Phase 1, you can activate this card's effect. If you do, it can attack your opponent directly this turn. Other monsters cannot attack during the turn you activate this effect.

card.name: Synchron Explorer
card.description: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 "Synchron" monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target, but its effects are negated.

card.name: Man-Eater Bug
card.description: FLIP: Target 1 monster on the field; destroy it.

card.name: Hayabusa Knight
card.description: This card can make a second attack during each Battle Phase.

card.name: Chainsaw Insect
card.description: At the end of the Damage Step, if this card attacked or was attacked: Your opponent draws 1 card.

card.name: Worm Apocalypse
card.description: FLIP: Target 1 Spell/Trap Card on the field; destroy that target.

card.name: Junk Synchron
card.description: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 Level 2 or lower monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target in Defense Position, but it has its effects negated.

card.name: Speed Warrior
card.description: Once per Battle Phase, if this card was Normal Summoned this turn (except during the Damage Step): You can make its ATK become double its original ATK, until the end of the Battle Phase.

card.name: Quillbolt Hedgehog
card.description: If this card is in your Graveyard: You can Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field. You must control a Tuner monster to activate and to resolve this effect.

card.name: X-Saber Galahad
card.description: If this card attacks an opponent's monster, this card gains 300 ATK during the Damage Step only. If this card is attacked by an opponent's monster, this card loses 500 ATK during the Damage Step only. When this card is selected as an attack target, you can Tribute another "Saber" monster to negate the attack.

card.name: Fortress Warrior
card.description: You take no battle damage from attacks involving this card. Once per turn, this card cannot be destroyed by battle.

card.name: Turret Warrior
card.description: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by Tributing 1 Warrior-Type monster, and if you do, it gains ATK equal to the Tributed monster's original ATK.

card.name: Twin-Sword Marauder
card.description: Once per Battle Phase, if this card attacks a Defense Position monster, it can make a second attack in a row. If this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing Battle Damage to your opponent.

card.name: Dark Tinker
card.description: When this card you control is sent to the Graveyard, look at the top card of your Deck. Return that card to either the top or the bottom of the Deck.

card.name: Quickdraw Synchron
card.description: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by sending 1 monster from your hand to the Graveyard. For a Synchro Summon, you can substitute this card for any 1 "Synchron" Tuner monster. Cannot be used as a Synchro Material, except for the Synchro Summon of a monster that lists a "Synchron" monster as a Tuner.

card.name: Half Shut
card.description: Target 1 face-up monster on the field; it cannot be destroyed by battle this turn, also its ATK is halved until the end of this turn.

card.name: Giant Trunade
card.description: Return all Spell and Trap Cards on the field to the hand.

card.name: Card Destruction
card.description: Both players discard as many cards as possible from their hands, then each player draws the same number of cards they discarded.

card.name: Reinforcement of the Army
card.description: Add 1 Level 4 or lower Warrior monster from your Deck to your hand.

card.name: The Warrior Returning Alive
card.description: Target 1 Warrior-Type monster in your Graveyard; add that target to your hand.

card.name: Banner of Courage
card.description: All monsters you control gain 200 ATK during your Battle Phase only.

card.name: Enemy Controller
card.description: Activate 1 of these effects.●Target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; change that target's battle position.●Tribute 1 monster, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; take control of that target until the End Phase.

card.name: Hammer Shot
card.description: Destroy the 1 face-up Attack Position monster that has the highest ATK. (If it's a tie, you get to choose.)

card.name: Monster Reincarnation
card.description: Discard 1 card, then target 1 monster in your GY; add it to your hand.

card.name: Synchro Boost
card.description: The equipped monster gains 500 ATK, and its Level is increased by 1.

card.name: Wild Tornado
card.description: Target 1 face-up card in the Spell & Trap Zone; destroy that face-up card, then, its controller can Set 1 Spell/Trap from their hand. If this Set card is destroyed and sent to the GY: Target 1 face-up card on the field; destroy that target.

card.name: Trap Hole
card.description: When your opponent Normal or Flip Summons 1 monster with 1000 or more ATK: Target that monster; destroy that target.

card.name: Dust Tornado
card.description: Target 1 Spell/Trap your opponent controls; destroy that target, then you can Set 1 Spell/Trap from your hand.

card.name: Raigeki Break
card.description: Discard 1 card, then target 1 card on the field; destroy it.

card.name: Rope of Life
card.description: When a monster(s) is destroyed by battle and sent to your Graveyard: Discard your entire hand (min.1), then target 1 of those monsters; Special Summon it, and if you do, it gains 800 ATK.

card.name: Secret Barrel
card.description: Inflict 200 damage to your opponent for each card in their hand and for each card they control.

card.name: Sakuretsu Armor
card.description: When an opponent's monster declares an attack: Target the attacking monster; destroy that target.

card.name: Threatening Roar
card.description: Your opponent cannot declare an attack this turn.

card.name: Rising Energy
card.description: Discard 1 card, then target 1 face-up monster on the field; that target gains 1500 ATK until the End Phase.

card.name: Defense Draw
card.description: During your opponent's turn, at damage calculation: Make the battle damage you take from this battle 0, and if you do, draw 1 card.

card.name: Junk Destroyer
card.description: "Junk Synchron" + 1 or more non-Tuner monstersWhen this card is Synchro Summoned: You can target cards on the field, up to the number of non-Tuner monsters used for the Synchro Summon of this card; destroy those targets.

card.name: X-Saber Urbellum
card.description: 1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monstersWhen this card inflicts Battle Damage to your opponent while they have 4 or more cards in their hand, place 1 random card from their hand on top of their Deck.

card.name: Gaia Knight, the Force of Earth
card.description: 1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monsters

card.name: X-Saber Wayne
card.description: 1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monstersWhen this card is Synchro Summoned, you can Special Summon 1 Level 4 or lower Warrior-Type monster from your hand.
